{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tag-tsx","path":"/tag/网络流/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"totalCount":1,"edges":[{"node":{"id":"26914f6f-8904-5b90-a480-2e9e27ae5fa1","excerpt":"<p>两人在一二分图上进行决策，初始状态为二分图的一个点，两人轮流沿边行动，不允许重复访问节点，无法移动者输。</p>\n<p>这样的问题称为二分图博弈。</p>\n<!--more-->\n<h2>二分图博弈</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>结论 1</strong></p>\n<p>起点 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>v</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">v</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">v</span></span></span></span></span> 是先手必胜的当且仅当其在所有最大匹配上。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>必要性</strong>：如果存在一个最大匹配 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">M</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">M</span></span></span></span></span> 使得 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>v</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">v</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">v</span></span></span></span></span> 不在其上，那么先手每次操作时，要么无路可走，要么走到了某个匹配点上（否则就找到了一条增广路），于是后手只需要每次走到 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">M</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">M</span></span></span></span></span>…</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"二分图博弈学习笔记","date":"25 March, 2020","cover":"/cover/54.jpg","tags":["二分图博弈","网络流"]},"parent":{"relativePath":"blog/algorithm/bipartite-graph-game.md"}}}]},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"memset0's blog","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"tag":"网络流"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}